                    "actionPointMin": 1,
                    "actionPointMax": 1,
                    "lines": [
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 0,
                            "text": "（镜头强行转到讲台侧，伴随声音）",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 1,
                            "text": "(**Julian老师** 推门而入。)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 2,
                            "text": "(他梳着侧分背头，穿着一件剪裁略显紧身的衬衫，眼镜上夹着一个橙色的滤镜片。)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "dialogId": "1_ap_2",
                    "day": 1,
                    "sequenceOrder": 0,
                    "actionPointMin": 2,
                    "actionPointMax": 2,
                    "lines": [
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 0,
                            "text": "(前台minna老师跟在他后面，将一沓橙色的书本放在讲台上。)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 1,
                            "text": "(在这个小城市里，她承包了我对都市丽人的一切想象。职业装，黑框眼镜，银色手链，淡淡的职业笑。)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "dialogId": "1_ap_3",
                    "day": 1,
                    "sequenceOrder": 0,
                    "actionPointMin": 3,
                    "actionPointMax": 3,
                    "lines": [
                        {
                            "speakerId": "teacher",
                            "characterName": "Julian",
                            "triggerOrder": 0,
                            "text": "hello everyone, welcome to……",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "teacher",
                            "characterName": "Julian",
                            "triggerOrder": 1,
                            "text": "Beyond english 暑期班",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "teacher",
                            "characterName": "Julian",
                            "triggerOrder": 2,
                            "text": "Look at me!",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 3,
                            "text": "！",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 4,
                            "text": "(minna老师适时的掩门走了（声音，关门吱~~）)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "dialogId": "1_ap_4",
                    "day": 1,
                    "sequenceOrder": 0,
                    "actionPointMin": 4,
                    "actionPointMax": 4,
                    "lines": [
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 0,
                            "text": "（他转身在白板上用马克笔狂草写下巨大的 **JULIAN**）（声音 粉笔）",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 1,
                            "text": "(I'm Julian. 你们暑期班的老师.)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "dialogId": "1_ap_5",
                    "day": 1,
                    "sequenceOrder": 0,
                    "actionPointMin": 5,
                    "actionPointMax": 5,
                    "lines": [
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 0,
                            "text": "(你们看这个词——**July**。一年中最好的日子。)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 1,
                            "text": "(在后面加了一个 **'an'**。在拉丁语的语境里，这意味着‘属于七月的’。)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "dialogId": "1_ap_6",
                    "day": 1,
                    "sequenceOrder": 0,
                    "actionPointMin": 6,
                    "actionPointMax": 6,
                    "lines": [
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 0,
                            "text": "(我留学的时候，在那边的海滩上，我就告诉自己，Julian，你要像七月的烈日一样，灼烧掉所有的平庸和胆怯！)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "dialogId": "1_ap_7",
                    "day": 1,
                    "sequenceOrder": 0,
                    "actionPointMin": 7,
                    "actionPointMax": 7,
                    "lines": [
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 0,
                            "text": "(英语是世界上最简单的语言！只要你敢喊出来，就能够超越它，超越自己。)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 1,
                            "text": "(来，Follow me!)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 2,
                            "text": "(Beyond English)",
                            "pictureId": "",
                            "playerPicture": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "speakerId": "player",
                            "characterName": "Me",
                            "triggerOrder": 3,
                            "text": "Beyond English",
                            "pictureId": "",
